{"tid":1021360,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"iKON宋允亨 MOMOLAND Daisy承認從3個月前開始戀愛！","createTime":"2019-02-14T07:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T09:30:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99c0c43f68d9453d2bb2dd097145a3e095cb1a5e","tid":1021360,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"今日（2月14日），韓媒體育首爾爆出iKON成員宋允亨和MOMOLAND成員Daisy戀愛。 「從三四個月前開始戀愛，兩人有空就會享受約會，彼此照料。 兩人的關係在幾名相關人士之間都是知道的事情，雖然行程繁忙，不能經常見面，但彼此珍惜。 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，雙方公司都表示：「確認後發表立場。 」隨後在爆出緋聞後的1個小時，Daisy方面承認：「從3個月前開始有好感，並開始戀愛。 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n95年出生的宋允亨是在隊裡擔當門面和副主唱，99年出生的Daisy在隊內擔當主舞和主Rapper。 兩人由歌壇前後輩關係發展成戀人關係？ 等待官方立場。<br />\n<br />\n*15:30 更新「最新消息」宋允亨所屬公司YG娛樂目前否認戀情：「兩人只是互有好感見過幾次面，並不是交往的關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/113965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F113965&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=e0a301d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/113965</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ebcbb61600a3091392b0d4c2a976111548663a","tid":1021360,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"NancyJewel我老婆 (MML佬) 點睇？"},{"pid":"b33f11e2bfef933b076731e1cd7ffdeee7e91e8b","tid":1021360,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86ebcbb61600a3091392b0d4c2a976111548663a","tid":1021360,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"NancyJewel我老婆 (MML佬) 點睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"冇感覺"}]}